## Fasta Syntax Definition File
## Language: fasta
## Filetypes: .fasta .fas .fa
## Maintainer: bioSyntax (info <at> bioSyntax.org)
## Version: v0.1

syntax "fasta" "\.fa|fas|fasta$"
magic "fasta file"

## Row 2: Nucleotides colors
icolor black,blue   "[A]"
icolor black,green  "[T]"
icolor black,red    "[C]"
icolor black,yellow "[G]"

## Row 1: Coloring headers
color brightyellow,black  "^>.*$" 
